      "comment": "WHIZZ MAXIMUS (7) resumed in a Special conditions H at Shepparton and finished seventh over 390m (22.76). Will be much improved. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MORNING DAWN (1) was below best at her last start when 7th at Shepparton following a win (22.65) there two back. Must be included in calculations. SAFELY (2) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Maiden three back before a placing at Shepparton the following run. Can hit the frame this time. BAMBI'S PRIDE (8) is on a run of three minor placings and will be thereabouts again.",
